text.tspan: This instance of IronData manages data belonging to Engineers Australia.

flowRoot.flowPara: IronData is an open source datawarehouse system licensed under the GNU GPL. All logos and trademarks relating to IronData are property of Looking Glass Solutions.
For more information on the system please refer to the links below.
The owner of data that IronData manages should come first in the list of links. The links concerning IronData itself, it's licensing and LGS should not be configurable.
Further links than these should be optional additions and configurable through the administration interface later.
